{"tid":1588122,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"記唔記得我地6月講過嘅野?","createTime":"2019-09-22T16:28:25.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-22T16:43:03.000Z","uid":114951,"like":6,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"c7d6b936fdf8e6b0bcb4bfd7dc32c1f25bf64928","tid":1588122,"uid":114951,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-22T16:28:25.000Z","msg":"首先睇番天琦講過咩<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/cXPf1XM.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FcXPf1XM.jpg&h=8eb22115&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n仲記唔記得我地6月個陣強調咩?<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">BE HUMBLE</span></span></strong><br />\n點都唔會割蓆<br />\n純粹有個小建議比大家<br />\n做任何決定，尤其神獸開波之前<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">深呼吸10秒<br />\n問一問理性嘅自己係咪要咁做</span></strong><br />\n之後再作決定<br />\n認同幫推<br />\n香港人加油<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2a032ca35340396c77b468c333f9ee45c2112916","tid":1588122,"uid":114951,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-22T16:29:31.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"f27f65b2372eb42df81ad46c69b8d1c24668e7f4","tid":1588122,"uid":114951,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-22T16:29:41.000Z","msg":"光復香港"},{"pid":"70011c5df9b944bbcfdc888306c70d8683af12bb","tid":1588122,"uid":114951,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-22T16:29:51.000Z","msg":"時代革命"},{"pid":"a65d250d481c5e0c00cbd364d69426c79695d139","tid":1588122,"uid":114951,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-22T16:30:01.000Z","msg":"香1港人一定要贏"},{"pid":"39fa4f5781565c359929c1451d6217977a560d83","tid":1588122,"uid":114951,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-22T16:30:45.000Z","msg":"十連推"},{"pid":"b6053a1126